Cell["For relational databases", "Title",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.780117430917284*^9, 
  3.780117444847677*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"aabaf366-a2ed-4543-9c0f-\
4f7d06891230"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["\<\
Find the data. Several websites are fed by databases. To get information from \
the web,just scrap it.\
\>", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.780117446670226*^9, 
  3.780117526057852*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"49693131-2fdd-4bda-846b-\
7e241a7a1e9b"],

Cell["\<\
If you want to get the information from the source, you need to discover \
where the backend is.\
\>", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.780117446670226*^9, 
  3.780117557082347*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"f2c822ce-77f8-489b-9d32-\
d263e0d9cb3d"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "For MySQL, SQLite, PostgreSQL and Microsoft SQL databases backend ",
 StyleBox["and assuming you only want to read (not write), ",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 "you can get information about the connectivity using DatabaseReference:"
}], "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.780117446670226*^9, 3.780117485367148*^9}, {
